title: Struck by a cosmic ray: Galactic particles may have forced a passenger jet to make an emergency landing
description: A cosmic ray from a faraway supernova explosion may have sent a packed passenger jet into free fall in late October, forcing an emergency landing.
content: A cosmic ray from a faraway supernova explosion may have sent a packed passenger jet into free fall in late October, forcing an emergency landing.
